metadata.description: A Timer for this and a Timer for that! Whether it is a clean up game or a calm tooth brush timer, my goal is to get you what you need! I am working to get this playlist filled to the brim with all the timers that you could want or need! I will send out updates as I add additional timers to this playlist that you can use!
